Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2D2F9C&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, who was killed by the \Ngreat organization GOD along with his father...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...revived as Kamen Rider X, thanks to his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Keisuke's lover, Ryouko, side with GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is Kiriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who fights against the mysterious GOD, Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The One-Eyed Monster's Kidnapping Operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,His skills are pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is strange. We're going the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Driver, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? This isn't the way to the kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there a kindergarten in these mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One-eyed monster, this is G.O.D General Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The first plan was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the children, and put all the parents in the city into panic mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One-eyed Radar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a one-eyed monster, Cyclops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}This morning, a bus carrying \Nkindergartners suddenly disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}We are going to continue the investigation of this incident.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be, possibly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, who is a Kaizorg, has many times more power than ordinary humans do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I though I only {\i1}lightly{\i0} slapped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightly? Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a passerby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you talking to yourself, so I was a bit worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You could hear my voice from outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...my ears are much better than ordinary people's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What a suspicious guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Don't tell me you're a modified human from Destron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Destron?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Destron was destroyed, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to look out for Destron as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry on and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The shop's closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember passing by that microbus around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I envy those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that voice just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very bad! \NAn accident occurred in the tunnel just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't go. This is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come to interfere with me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really an ally of GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard... you're a cyborg of GOD aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a member of the GOD radical group...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One-eyed monster, Cyclops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Cyclops is a one-eyed monster who appears in Greek myths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}He is an invincible and frightening monster that catches and eats humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it, you guys were behind this after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster of GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You two. I'll take your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,One-eyed Radar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dreaming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're that woman from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is even happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's similar looking to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but she's a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you and Ryouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am, I assure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm not your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The allies of GOD...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are using the underground of the tunnel as their base...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they're kidnapping little boys and girls,\N they're plotting something scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It is your mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...to destroy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Tachibana Toubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be the President of the Rider Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider #1...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,#2...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,V3...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And Riderman, #4. I know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not any one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is... Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was killed along with my father, who was my only blood relative...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...by an organization called GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And revived as a modified human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And, my other name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your other name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the GOD General Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke and Tachibana Toubei. They will get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring out the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed with the Alpha Plan before we get interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you are going to be preserved as frozen humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When this country is under \Nthe command of GOD one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be reborn as slaves of GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Let go of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the freezing process.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Process successful. Bring them out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you shall become slaves of GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A truck is heading towards the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why isn't it moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's not going back either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Hey, the ground is moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! What am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you telling me I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is GOD's base, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've captured the truck's driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dirty guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Put him in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember this face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To come sneaking all the way into GOD's base...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...takes guts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke's entered our base, and he freed the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an ally of GOD, I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still call yourself a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving the children to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider's Ridol, by pressing the "right" switch, \Ncan turn into the Ridol Rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider X, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One-eyed Radar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The children who were frozen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...turned back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me. She did it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider! X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You should all study hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The frightening cyborg of GOD, that one-eyed monster was defeated by X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the children were able to go back to their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the wall between X Rider and GOD is thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Be strong! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Our X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(18,0)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"The Japanese Islands Fragmentation Plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.15,0:24:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.15,0:24:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider